 Of course! That=E2=80=99s what it=E2=80=99s worth! That's why you bought i=
t! (For $80.)=09You book $20 of profits, charge performance fees, etc.And t=
hen, oh, you know.=C2=A0Sometimes you sell the thing a week later for $100=
=C2=A0and everything is great.
