  [3] Not legal or investing advice! But would I do that? Yes.


  [4] Meanwhile everyone who has emailed me to say =E2=80=9Cactually there=
=E2=80=99s a good business case for Trump Media=E2=80=9D has gone on to say=
 =E2=80=9Cit would be a good way for foreign governments to bribe Donald Tr=
ump if he becomes president again,=E2=80=9D which is true, but also kind of=
 a conspiracy theory.


  [5] My answer is always no, for what it's worth, but empirically other pe=
ople seem to have different utility functions.


