</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I tell you what: If I could make the p=
rice of a publicly traded stock double just by <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35668194.286303/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLm=
