ackground-color: #ccc;">tweeting a cartoon of a guy leaning forward in a ch=
air</a>, and if I could make <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/35668194.286303/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2Fy=
